longBusinessSummary: Globe Photos, Inc. acquires, sells, licenses, and merchandises classic and contemporary limited edition photographic images and reproductions, with a focus on iconic celebrity images in the United States. The company offers its products through auctions, third-party galleries, art consultants, interior decorators, bricks and mortar locations, and specialty and big box retailers, as well as directly to consumers and through various online outlets. It also produces, sells, and licenses sports prints, lithographs, and other related items. Globe Photos, Inc. is headquartered in Las Vegas, Nevada.
